title: Openstreetmap, Saarland Roadways, Germany, 2008
name: Openstreetmap, Saarland Roadways, Germany, 2008
description: This data was provided by Openstreetmaps and shows detailed information about the roadways in Berlin, Germany. Roadways contain attributed information about the road type (Primary, secondary, path, highway, etc...) and the road name when available. Data was uploaded as a poly line shape file. There is also an attribute called ‚Äòoneway‚Äô which is a one way flag. If the value is 0, it is a two way road, if the value of the one way flag is 1, the road is a one way road.
